<D>__{that's pretty wild, mom.}
<C>__{rochelle}
<D>__{right?}
<P>__{(notices that kate hasn't touched her drink)}
<D>__{what's wrong, honey? think i forgot how to mix `em?}
<C>__{kate}
<D>__{i told you i just wanted water.}
<C>__{rochelle}
<D>__{oh, please! where i'm from, "no" means "yes."}
<P>__{(to charlie)}
<D>__{am i right or am i right?}
<C>__{charlie}
<P>__{(forcing it)}
<D>__{huh huh...}
<C>__{kate}
<D>__{that's actually why i wanted to come up, mom.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{i stopped drinking.}
<A>__{rochelle laughs then realizes kate and charlie aren't joking.}
<C>__{rochelle}
<P>__{(quickly serious)}
<D>__{are you telling me i'm going to be a grandma?}
<A>__{rochelle tears up with joy.}
<C>__{rochelle }
<D>__{oh that's so exciting! i'm gonna be a grandma!}
<P>__{(to charlie)}
<D>__{and you know that "no drinking when you're pregnant" thing is just a myth. i drank plenty when i was pregnant with kate and look how she turned out!}
<A>__{beat.}
<C>__{kate}
<D>__{i'm not pregnant, mom.}
